Short:        Candle Amiga Demo
Author:       Candle
Type:         demo/aga
Architecture: m68k-amigaos
Requirements: A500 or better, A1200/30 or faster recommended

Slighty modified and recompiled in 2008, the intro was made in 1996 but
was never released. Yes, coded in Amos. (Angel's handle is misspelled in
the scroller as "Angle".)

Just extract the file/files into the same directory, your Candle directory ;-)
and run the executable file.
                                                                                
